tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE warehouse_inventory (
    product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(50),
    quantity INT,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE transaction_log (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    transaction_date DATE,
    quantity_changed INT,
    user_id INT
)
CREATE TABLE warehouse_inventory (id INT, product_name TEXT, quantity INT, last_updated TIMESTAMP)
CREATE TABLE inventory_transactions (transaction_id INT, product_id INT, transaction_type TEXT, quantity_changed INT, transaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP)
CREATE TABLE inventory_audit_logs (log_id INT, transaction_id INT, product_id INT, action_taken TEXT, action_timestamp TIMESTAMP)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_transactions (
  transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  transaction_type VARCHAR(255),
  transaction_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_inventory (
  product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_name VARCHAR(255),
  quantity INT,
  last_updated TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  transaction_id INT,
  log_message TEXT,
  logged_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_audit (
  audit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  transaction_id INT,
  updated_quantity INT,
  audit_reason TEXT,
  audit_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_inventory (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    quantity INT,
    unit_price DECIMAL,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    quantity INT,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE products (
    product_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    category VARCHAR(50),
    price DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    role VARCHAR(50),
    created_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE audit_logs (
    log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    action VARCHAR(50),
    action_date TIMESTAMP,
    performed_by VARCHAR(50)
)
